==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unbone
<hw>Un*bone"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>bone</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>To deprive of bones, as meat; to bone.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To twist about, as if boneless.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unbonnet</ent>⟦br⟧
